2017年6月9月，[[英國獨立黨|英國獨立黨]]黨魁[[保羅·勞塔爾|保羅·勞塔爾]]就[[2017年英國大選|2017年英國大選]]表現惡劣而引咎請辭，繼而觸發'''2017年英國獨立黨黨魁選舉'''（{{lang-en|2017 UK Independence Party leadership election}}）<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/election-2017-40220074|title=Election results 2017: Paul Nuttall quits as UKIP leader|work=BBC News|date=2017-06-09|accessdate=2017-06-14|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111204123/https://www.bbc.com/news/election-2017-40220074|dead-url=no}}</ref>。三日後，前主席{{tsl|en|Steve Crowther|史蒂夫·高特}}獲指定為代理黨魁<ref name="Crowther">{{cite web|url=http://www.northdevongazette.co.uk/news/election/north-devon-s-steve-crowther-becomes-ukip-leader-1-5058727|title=North Devon's Steve Crowther becomes UKIP leader|publisher={{tsl|en|North Devon Gazette||North Devon Gazette}}|date=2017-06-12|accessdate=2017-06-14|archive-date=2017-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170913130038/http://www.northdevongazette.co.uk/news/election/north-devon-s-steve-crowther-becomes-ukip-leader-1-5058727|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

8月11日，獨立黨確定11名候選人競逐黨魁一職<ref name="candidatesbbc">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-40902796|title=Anne Marie Waters: Anti-Islam candidate to stand for UKIP leadership|publisher=BBC|date=2017-08-11|accessdate=2020-09-13|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112024049/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-40902796|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但及後共有7人退選或改為支持其他候選人<ref name="The Independent">{{Cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/leadership-election-torquay-paul-nuttall-jane-collins-david-coburn-ben-walker-marion-mason-anne-a7926051.html|title=Four Ukip candidates unite in joint leadership bid to defeat anti-Islam candidate|date=2017-09-02|work=The Independent|access-date=2017-09-02|language=en|archive-date=2019-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190427130133/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/leadership-election-torquay-paul-nuttall-jane-collins-david-coburn-ben-walker-marion-mason-anne-a7926051.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最終{{tsl|en|Henry Bolton (British politician)|亨利·波頓}}得票30%，當選新任獨立黨黨魁<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-41447568|title=Henry Bolton elected UKIP leader|publisher=BBC|date=2017-09-29|accessdate=2020-09-13|archive-date=2017-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170929151110/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-41447568|dead-url=no}}</ref>

